data.description: Diamond in the rough! Tons of potential throughout this 4 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home. Shop behind converted into a 4 bedroom ADU - income potential? Bring your hammer and with a little elbow grease make this fixer fabulous! 2014/2015- all new insulation and drywall, new 200-Amp panel, all new wiring, some new plumbing. Easy access to freeway with shops, restaurants, and parks nearby.
